ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係聽話咁快就入齊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔入黎 = 潛水唔敢入<br />\n入黎 = 真係聽話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學你搬龍門大法啫<br />\n你做得時我唔撚做得呀風紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講黎講去都講唔撚到點搬法<br />\n咪撚貼D九唔搭八圖再講多十次你搬龍門就當係至得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到而家，我都仲係話我肯定強姦有出現過<br />\n差佬有冇拉錯人唔小心打死犯但唔知<br />\n但就仲覺得死於自殺既機會係最大<br />\n<br />\n你條柒頭等差佬拉個女仔報假案先<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>鞭屍</strong></span></span>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拉左個疑犯就坐定粒六開個鞭屍post<br />\n[binc]係時候回顧連登神探精彩推理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/236984/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/236984/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd517b77f08a84f2eb213c6404e038c37adca80d"